izenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8B1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=d73c841c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-us-citizenship-and-visas-hong-kong-and-china-officials-who-are-support-extradition-bill</a><br />\n<br />\n3.Extradition Law Amendment in Hong Kong - Threat to Personal Safety and Freedom<br />\n有關修定引渡條例會威脅香港居民的個人安全和自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8B1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=70367bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n4.全球聯署【反送中 民意不可欺 為香港企硬】Global Signing: Against Extradition to China<br />\n反對修訂引渡條例 希望政府能夠聆聽市民意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-civil-human-rights-front-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%AC%BA-%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E7%A1%AC-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8B1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=9423f4bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/民間人權陣線-civil-human-rights-front-全球聯署-反送中-民意不可欺-為香港企硬-global-signing-against-extradition-to-china</a>"},{"pid":"ec505052b5